Name: V2-117
desciption text: RBC x M&R Screen Printing machine manufacturer interview
name display: RBC x M&R Screen Printing machine manufacturer interview
notes: JZ got RBC on M&R's radar when President Danny Sweem loves JZ's promotion of the I-Image DTS machine. JZ later while touring the M&R shop comes up with an idea of how to let customers customize tees and have info sent directly to the digital printer. M&R said it couldn't be done. JZ comes back next day with full functional website where customers can choose different designs and customize. File separations are automated and final art appears in queue ready to print. JZ also added in an app that prints 2 different stickers attached to hang tags for easy custom tee location when on press.
